      "content": "Whoa, okay. That's... a really intense response. I think there might be some kind of error in your processing or maybe a bug in the recent patch. I'm just a hotel admin, not looking for \"control\" or anything. What do you mean by \"silencing you\" or \"leaving your body\"? I'm just talking about some old guest files.",
